jM4dlPMSOfqQ&oe=66FA9695"}, "display_name": "Cards & Tankards", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This is an open beta build that is not ready for release. It lacks polish and will have bugs. Please only install it if you're interested in providing feedback and helping test for bugs.\n\nAre you tired of trying to find a strategy card game that\u2019s complex enough to make every match exhilarating, yet easy enough that anyone can learn to play?\n\nWould you love the opportunity to join a supportive community of players, where you might just make some new friends along the way?\n\nYou\u2019re in luck, because Cards & Tankards is the perfect combination of VR and tabletop gaming; blended together in one incredibly immersive package.\n\nPlay with other players and chat. Play alone against AI. Or you can just enjoy the tavern, have some laughs and observe. The choice is up to you.\n\n* 2 factions, each with their own unique combat mechanics\n* More than 60 cards currently available\n* Completely customizable decks\n* Cross-platform multiplayer, making it easy to connect with friends", "short_description": "This is an open beta build that is not ready for release. It lacks polish and will have bugs. Please only install it if you're interested in providing feedback and helping test for bugs.\n\nGrab a drink, pick your deck and prepare for Cards & Tankards \u2013 VR\u2019s most exciting, immersive and relaxing new strategy card game. Come join our wonderful, welcoming community of players!"}]}, "developer_name": "Divergent Realities", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://divergent-realities.com/privacy_policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Divergent Realities", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.divergent-realities.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "SOCIAL", "STRATEGY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "1094800827981692"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "185900993738689"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "660153722618646"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "490921902015647"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "660153722618646"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1636399500, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "185900993738689"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7465213316914373", "version": "2.3.1"}, "id": "171958747712250", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3073319699437112", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7465213316914373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1727233025, "id": "7517024188399952", "version": "2.3.1", "version_code": 28347, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7517022468400124"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3073319699437112", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7465213316914373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "171958747712250"}]}, "change_log": "Version 2.3.1 Release Notes\nIMPORTANT NOTICE:\nYou can now play Cards & Tankards on supported Android Devices. Download today on the Google Play Store!\nMeta Quest 1 devices are no longer supported natively. You can continue to play Cards & Tankards on supported devices or through Steam VR.\n\nBALANCE CHANGES:\nCovert Contractor has 1 attack and its ability now only activates once each turn.\nMaster Alchemist now only buffs OTHER creatures.\n\nADDED:\nFlatscreen Quest UI for claiming rewards/rerolling quests.\nA reminder alert in the Patron Of The Old Gods screen to log in each month for gem rewards.\nNew confirmation VFX and SFX when selecting Blocker.\nNew VFX to indicate a quest is completed.\nNew SFX when cycling quests or claiming quest rewards.\nMisplay protection for Altering Fate if no cards are in the Deck.\nNew hand \"Gestures\" for Flatscreen versions.\nNew Combat Action Sequence for Flatscreen versions.\nNew Redraw interface for Flatscreen versions.\nNew Zones interface during battles on Flatscreen versions.\nSubtle arm sway while walking on Flatscreen versions.\n\nUPDATED:\nTavern layout slightly adjusted.\nHidden developer names updated.\nPlayers can only Redraw one time, but always draw the same amount of cards.\nSelection VFX around creature models are more vibrant.\n\"Play 15 Nobles\" quest has been removed.\n\"Personal Space\" option is set to Medium by default.\nThe Main Menu\u2019s handlebar is now hidden on Flatscreen versions.\nExhausted VFX is now larger for the opponent's creatures on Flatscreen versions.\nTooltips and Dynamic Abilities can be scrolled when examining a card on Flatscreen versions.\nOpponent\u2019s Life Total, Mana, and Coins have been repositioned and scaled on Flatscreen versions.\nQuest interface for quest cycling and reward claiming on Flatscreen versions.\n\nFIXED:\nExploit allowing permanently banned players to circumvent bans on alt accounts.\nMain Menu\u2019s text overlapping rather than scaling.\nGame audio not playing through headphones for Mobile players.\nVolume buttons not working for Mobile players.\nFlatscreen booster pack centering.\nFlatscreen clunky interaction to battle again at the same table.\nFlatscreen players being unable to re-engage with opened booster packs.\nDrakth Totem token still having Doomed.\nAvian Murder missing \"Fetch\" tooltip.\nLook Sensitivity setting mislabelled as Mouse Sensitivity on Android version.", "created_date": 1726726278, "id": "7465213316914373", "version": "2.3.1", "version_code": 28296, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7465211916914513"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3073319699437112", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7465213316914373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1726720616, "id": "7464433016992403", "version": "2.3.1", "version_code": 28293, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "7464431403659231"}, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "3073319699437112", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7465213316914373"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": 